						               													<description>Pizza Party Throwdown, the crazy new pizza toppings game! Players have 30 seconds to toss their &amp;ldquo;ingredients&amp;rdquo; onto the rotating pizza game board. It&amp;rsquo;s a rush against time to land your ingredients on the pizza before it finishes &amp;ldquo;baking!&amp;rdquo; Each player selects their color-coded ingredient &amp;ndash; like pepperoni, peppers, mushrooms and of course, anchovies! Launch it onto the pizza using the special pizza chef launcher game piece.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Great for all ages! Three different challenges deliver various levels of difficulty, like trying to fill only half of your pizza, or land your ingredients on only one slice! Includes rotating pizza game board with built-in timer, four launchers and 32 ingredients.&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game Pizza Party Throwdown there are three different ways to play but each one consists of players using catapult-like launchers to toss their ingredients onto the spinning cardboard pizza before the pizza stops spinning. In most cases, whoever has the most of their toppings on the pizza wins. Different play modes include simply having to put all of your toppings on the pizza first, putting all of your toppings on only one half of the pizza first, or putting two different toppings onto two different quarter sections of the pizza first.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
